            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">1 Chronicles 29:9</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Then the people rejoiced, for that they offered willingly, because with perfect heart they offered willingly to the LORD: and David the king also rejoiced with great joy.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">And the people rejoice because of their offering willingly, for with a perfect heart they have offered willingly to Jehovah; and also David the king hath rejoiced -- great joy.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Then the people<S>5971</S> rejoiced<S>8055</S>, for that they offered willingly<S>5068</S>, because with a perfect<S>8003</S> heart<S>3820</S> they offered willingly<S>5068</S> to Jehovah<S>3068</S>: and David<S>1732</S> the king<S>4428</S> also rejoiced<S>8055</S> with great<S>1419</S> joy<S>8057</S>.</span></div>
